### DL 최종 승인 (TL_APPROVED → APPROVED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/kms/approval/{{articleId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{dlToken}}

{
  "approverId": 1774590584056408,
  "reviewComment": "최종 승인합니다."
}

### DL 반려 (TL_APPROVED → REJECTED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/kms/approval/{{articleId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{dlToken}}

{
  "reviewComment": "정책에 부합하지 않는 내용이 포함되어 있습니다. 수정 후 재제출해주세요."
}
